name: Leo Williams
interests: Outdoor adventures, creating art, travel, cooking, reading
summary:
Leo Williams is a 35-year-old straight man of Black African descent who currently lives in Los Angeles, California. He is 6'2" tall, a University of Texas at Austin graduate, and works in the healthcare industry as a physical therapist. Leo speaks English and Spanish. His values center on kindness, straightforwardness, and empathy. His interests include outdoor adventures, creating art, travelling, cooking, and reading. He subscribes to agnostic beliefs, exhibits moderate political views, and identifies as an ENFJ. Leo doesn't smoke or use drugs and occasionally drinks. He is active and enjoys working out. 

He's looking for a life partner who is also monogamous. While Leo doesn't have children, he wishes to have them in the future. On the light-hearted side, he is a Leo and a dog-lover. Leo's ideal partner, aged between 27 and 40, shares his stance on smoking, drinking, and drugs. She also values an active lifestyle, doesn't have children, but wants them in the future.
